request.description:
Create a new user account.

## Request Fields
- **email**: User's email address (required)
- **password**: Minimum 6 characters (required)
- **first_name**: User's first name (required)
- **last_name**: User's last name (required)

## Request Examples

### ✅ Valid Request
```json
{
    "user": {
        "email": "john.doe@example.com",
        "password": "SecurePass123!",
        "first_name": "John",
        "last_name": "Doe"
    }
}
```

### ❌ Invalid Email
```json
{
    "user": {
        "email": "invalid-email",
        "password": "SecurePass123!",
        "first_name": "John",
        "last_name": "Doe"
    }
}
```

### ❌ Password Too Short
```json
{
    "user": {
        "email": "john.doe@example.com",
        "password": "123",
        "first_name": "John",
        "last_name": "Doe"
    }
}
```

